1
00:00:04,350 --> 00:00:05,860
This weather's great!

2
00:00:05,860 --> 00:00:09,950
If we keep going this way,
we should see the Marine base soon!

3
00:00:09,940 --> 00:00:12,700
Wow, Koby! You're incredible!

4
00:00:12,700 --> 00:00:14,330
We're really gonna get there?

5
00:00:14,330 --> 00:00:15,450
Of course!

6
00:00:15,450 --> 00:00:18,140
Sailors should at least
be able to navigate!

7
00:00:20,210 --> 00:00:23,290
This is no time
to be laughing, Luffy.

8
00:00:23,290 --> 00:00:25,380
He's being held captive there.

9
00:00:25,760 --> 00:00:28,150
The infamous Pirate Hunter...

10
00:00:29,050 --> 00:00:31,390
Roronoa Zoro!

11
00:00:34,640 --> 00:00:40,460
The man slashes up his bounties
like a bloodthirsty beast.

12
00:00:41,810 --> 00:00:45,530
People say he's a demon
in human form!

13
00:02:52,990 --> 00:02:54,400
We're here!

14
00:02:54,400 --> 00:02:56,590
We made it to the Marine town!

15
00:03:01,160 --> 00:03:05,540
C-C'mon, Luffy! You can't be
serious about recruiting him!

16
00:03:05,540 --> 00:03:08,570
I haven't decided yet,
but if he's a good guy...

17
00:03:08,570 --> 00:03:10,960
He was arrested
because he's not a good guy!

18
00:03:14,630 --> 00:03:15,470
Yum!

19
00:03:16,330 --> 00:03:19,180
So this Zoro guy's at the base?

20
00:03:24,560 --> 00:03:27,400
Maybe we shouldn't mention
Zoro around here...

21
00:03:28,210 --> 00:03:29,880
Well, let's check out the base.

22
00:03:29,880 --> 00:03:31,650
You're gonna be a Marine, right?

23
00:03:31,650 --> 00:03:35,030
Y-Yes... But I'm not really ready yet...

24
00:03:35,030 --> 00:03:39,360
They say a man named
Captain Morgan is at this base.

25
00:03:45,910 --> 00:03:47,540
This town is hilarious!

26
00:03:47,540 --> 00:03:49,250
It's strange...

27
00:03:49,250 --> 00:03:52,920
I get Zoro, but why are they
afraid of a Marine captain's name?

28
00:03:53,840 --> 00:03:56,840
I'm getting a bad feeling about this…

29
00:03:56,840 --> 00:03:59,340
You sure they weren't
just really excited?

30
00:03:59,340 --> 00:04:00,930
That clearly wasn't it!

31
00:04:02,850 --> 00:04:04,390
Alright! We're here!

32
00:04:05,220 --> 00:04:07,390
I finally made it!

33
00:04:08,380 --> 00:04:10,760
I guess this is where
we part ways, Luffy.

34
00:04:10,760 --> 00:04:12,650
We didn't know each other long, but...

35
00:04:12,650 --> 00:04:13,270
Huh?

36
00:04:13,270 --> 00:04:14,690
There we go!

37
00:04:14,690 --> 00:04:16,650
Luffy! What in the world
are you doing?!

38
00:04:16,650 --> 00:04:19,360
Now, where's this demon?!

39
00:04:19,360 --> 00:04:21,660
He wouldn't be out in the open.

40
00:04:21,660 --> 00:04:23,870
I'm sure he's in a cell or something.

41
00:04:23,870 --> 00:04:24,950
Found him!

42
00:04:24,950 --> 00:04:26,200
Perfect!

43
00:04:28,660 --> 00:04:29,830
See! There he is!

44
00:04:29,830 --> 00:04:32,210
I'm telling you! He wouldn't be out–

45
00:04:37,880 --> 00:04:41,360
A black bandana and a bellyband...

46
00:04:43,130 --> 00:04:46,270
That's Roronoa Zoro!

47
00:04:46,270 --> 00:04:48,940
It'll be easy to get him out
if we untie those ropes!

48
00:04:48,940 --> 00:04:53,020
D-Don't be stupid! We don't know
what he'd do if we set him loose!

49
00:04:53,020 --> 00:04:56,190
I bet he'd try to kill you, Luffy!

50
00:04:56,190 --> 00:04:58,190
Don't worry! I'm tough!

51
00:04:58,190 --> 00:05:00,660
Is this guy for real?!

52
00:05:01,160 --> 00:05:02,370
Hey, you two!

53
00:05:04,200 --> 00:05:05,540
You're annoying me.

54
00:05:08,160 --> 00:05:09,160
Beat it!

55
00:05:10,460 --> 00:05:14,040
Luffy! You're a goner
if he joins your crew!

56
00:05:24,970 --> 00:05:27,220
Oh no! Luffy, you have to stop her!

57
00:05:27,220 --> 00:05:29,050
She'll be killed!

58
00:05:30,230 --> 00:05:31,100
What?

59
00:05:31,100 --> 00:05:32,980
You must be hungry!

60
00:05:32,980 --> 00:05:35,060
I made you some rice balls.

61
00:05:35,060 --> 00:05:37,850
You got a death wish,
kid? Go home!

62
00:05:37,850 --> 00:05:40,400
You haven't eaten a thing
this whole time, mister.

63
00:05:40,860 --> 00:05:41,610
Here!

64
00:05:41,610 --> 00:05:46,330
It's my first time making them,
but I worked real hard!

65
00:05:47,870 --> 00:05:49,830
I'm not hungry!

66
00:05:49,830 --> 00:05:51,370
Now, stop bugging me and leave!

67
00:05:51,370 --> 00:05:52,000
But...

68
00:05:52,000 --> 00:05:54,250
I don't want them!
Don't make me kick your ass!

69
00:05:55,000 --> 00:05:57,380
Picking on little girls?

70
00:06:00,620 --> 00:06:04,220
You seem surprisingly well, Roronoa Zoro.

71
00:06:04,220 --> 00:06:06,600
What's with the weird
guy down there?

72
00:06:06,600 --> 00:06:07,680
Thank goodness!

73
00:06:07,680 --> 00:06:09,520
He must be with the Marines!

74
00:06:09,520 --> 00:06:11,100
That girl will be in good hands!

75
00:06:11,600 --> 00:06:14,980
Oh? Well aren't those some
tasty-looking rice balls?

76
00:06:14,980 --> 00:06:16,150
Don't...!

77
00:06:18,610 --> 00:06:19,400
Too sweet!

78
00:06:19,900 --> 00:06:21,360
You made them all sugary!

79
00:06:21,360 --> 00:06:23,520
Rice balls are made with salt! Salt!

80
00:06:23,530 --> 00:06:26,870
But I thought sweet
might taste better...

81
00:06:27,740 --> 00:06:30,910
Take this! And this!

82
00:06:28,660 --> 00:06:29,870
Stop it! Stop it!

83
00:06:30,290 --> 00:06:32,120
H-How can he be so cruel?

84
00:06:36,830 --> 00:06:41,550
I-I worked so hard to make those...

85
00:06:43,720 --> 00:06:46,180
Didn't you get the memo?

86
00:06:46,590 --> 00:06:50,100
"Those caught aiding
criminals will be executed!

87
00:06:50,100 --> 00:06:51,970
– Captain Morgan of the Marines."

88
00:06:54,480 --> 00:06:57,560
So, even the brats here know
how scary Daddy can be.

89
00:06:57,940 --> 00:06:59,190
"Daddy"?

90
00:06:59,190 --> 00:07:01,860
He must be Captain Morgan's son!

91
00:07:02,230 --> 00:07:04,320
You. Throw the kid over the wall.

92
00:07:04,320 --> 00:07:05,110
Sir?!

93
00:07:06,240 --> 00:07:08,950
I said, throw her over the wall!

94
00:07:08,950 --> 00:07:10,740
Got a problem following orders?

95
00:07:10,740 --> 00:07:12,370
Don't make me tell Daddy!

96
00:07:12,370 --> 00:07:13,910
Y-Yes, sir... Right away!

97
00:07:15,620 --> 00:07:16,790
No...

98
00:07:16,790 --> 00:07:17,790
No!

99
00:07:24,510 --> 00:07:26,380
Th-Thanks...

100
00:07:26,380 --> 00:07:27,920
Are you okay, Luffy?!

101
00:07:28,900 --> 00:07:30,640
Did you get hurt?

102
00:07:30,640 --> 00:07:33,180
What a horrible guy...

103
00:07:33,180 --> 00:07:34,850
Does anything hurt?

104
00:07:35,270 --> 00:07:36,270
You bastard...

105
00:07:40,560 --> 00:07:44,110
You sure are dead set
on staying alive.

106
00:07:44,110 --> 00:07:47,280
Yeah! I'm gonna
survive the whole month!

107
00:07:47,280 --> 00:07:49,370
Well, good luck with that.

108
00:07:52,370 --> 00:07:54,200
Only ten more days!

109
00:07:54,200 --> 00:07:56,960
Assuming you live that long!

110
00:07:58,870 --> 00:08:02,210
How can someone
be so cruel, Luffy?!

111
00:08:02,550 --> 00:08:04,420
Huh?! He's gone?!

112
00:08:06,670 --> 00:08:08,930
I hear you're a bad guy.

113
00:08:08,930 --> 00:08:10,600
What are you still doing here?

114
00:08:10,600 --> 00:08:13,130
Getting put out here for all to see...

115
00:08:13,130 --> 00:08:14,640
Are you actually strong?

116
00:08:14,640 --> 00:08:16,020
What's it to you?!

117
00:08:19,100 --> 00:08:21,940
If it were me, I'd probably
starve to death in three days!

118
00:08:21,940 --> 00:08:24,480
Then you lack willpower.

119
00:08:25,320 --> 00:08:28,240
I will live through this...

120
00:08:28,240 --> 00:08:29,360
I swear it!

121
00:08:30,910 --> 00:08:32,240
You're a pretty weird guy!

122
00:08:32,240 --> 00:08:32,870
Wait!

123
00:08:32,870 --> 00:08:33,490
Huh?

124
00:08:34,540 --> 00:08:36,580
Could you... get that for me?

125
00:08:37,830 --> 00:08:40,080
You wanna eat this?

126
00:08:40,080 --> 00:08:41,920
It's more of a mud ball now.

127
00:08:41,920 --> 00:08:43,540
Just shut up and give it here!

128
00:08:50,180 --> 00:08:51,640
Told you so.

129
00:08:51,640 --> 00:08:53,180
It was good.

130
00:08:54,060 --> 00:08:55,640
Thanks for the food.

131
00:08:57,770 --> 00:08:59,270
Really?!

132
00:08:59,850 --> 00:09:01,100
Yeah!

133
00:09:01,100 --> 00:09:03,480
He ate every last bite!

134
00:09:03,480 --> 00:09:04,820
I'm so glad!

135
00:09:04,820 --> 00:09:08,440
But then, is Zoro really
as bad as they say?

136
00:09:08,440 --> 00:09:10,450
He's not!

137
00:09:10,450 --> 00:09:14,950
After all, he let himself get
tied to that cross in my place...

138
00:09:14,950 --> 00:09:16,950
Huh? What do you mean?

139
00:09:16,950 --> 00:09:19,710
It's all Helmeppo's fault.

140
00:09:20,870 --> 00:09:23,310
He's Captain Morgan's son...

141
00:09:24,790 --> 00:09:26,500
Outta the way!

142
00:09:26,500 --> 00:09:30,550
Make way for my precious,
adorable little pooch!

143
00:09:30,550 --> 00:09:33,090
Get in the way,
and you get executed!

144
00:09:39,770 --> 00:09:41,350
No! Stop that!

145
00:09:41,350 --> 00:09:42,850
Hey, you!

146
00:09:42,850 --> 00:09:46,070
You got some kinda problem
with my sweet little pup?!

147
00:09:46,070 --> 00:09:47,530
Rika! Stop that!

148
00:09:47,530 --> 00:09:49,240
We'll get in trouble!

149
00:09:56,080 --> 00:09:57,580
Oh, crap!

150
00:09:57,580 --> 00:09:59,200
He's in for it now!

151
00:10:02,250 --> 00:10:06,670
Helmeppo punches
and kicks him while he's tied up!

152
00:10:07,290 --> 00:10:09,880
I... I...

153
00:10:09,880 --> 00:10:12,170
So that's what happened...

154
00:10:14,590 --> 00:10:15,720
I'm hungry!

155
00:10:15,720 --> 00:10:18,010
Treat us all to a free meal!

156
00:10:19,770 --> 00:10:21,810
Hey! Bring me a drink already!

157
00:10:21,810 --> 00:10:22,810
Oh, yes.

158
00:10:23,310 --> 00:10:27,110
To alleviate my boredom,
I'll have Zoro executed tomorrow.

159
00:10:27,570 --> 00:10:29,400
Save the date, everyone!

160
00:10:38,780 --> 00:10:40,290
Wh-What the hell are you doing?!

161
00:10:40,290 --> 00:10:42,410
Luffy! Please stop!

162
00:10:42,410 --> 00:10:44,120
This guy's scum!

163
00:10:44,120 --> 00:10:46,170
Y-You hit me!

164
00:10:46,170 --> 00:10:48,630
I'm Captain Morgan's son, you know!

165
00:10:48,630 --> 00:10:49,800
So what?!

166
00:10:50,130 --> 00:10:52,760
When I tell Daddy, he'll execute you!

167
00:10:52,760 --> 00:10:54,840
Fight me yourself!

168
00:10:54,840 --> 00:10:56,640
Luffy! Calm down!

169
00:10:56,640 --> 00:10:58,640
Do you want the Marines
as your enemy?!

170
00:10:58,640 --> 00:11:00,390
I've made up my mind, Koby!

171
00:10:59,720 --> 00:11:00,390
Huh?

172
00:11:01,720 --> 00:11:02,730
I'm...

173
00:11:03,480 --> 00:11:05,520
gonna get Zoro to join my crew!

174
00:11:09,360 --> 00:11:10,440
I am...

175
00:11:11,650 --> 00:11:12,570
great!

176
00:11:12,570 --> 00:11:13,570
Yes!

177
00:11:13,570 --> 00:11:15,820
You're exactly right,
Captain Morgan, sir!

178
00:11:15,820 --> 00:11:20,030
Then why are the recent tributes
to me falling short?

179
00:11:20,030 --> 00:11:24,750
W-Well, the citizens' wallets
do have their limits...

180
00:11:25,120 --> 00:11:28,040
It's a matter of respect.

181
00:11:28,670 --> 00:11:30,460
Wouldn't you agree?

182
00:11:32,210 --> 00:11:33,670
Daddy!

183
00:11:34,220 --> 00:11:37,970
I want you to kill someone for me!

184
00:11:43,180 --> 00:11:46,310
You again? You sure have
a lot of free time.

185
00:11:46,310 --> 00:11:48,770
I'll untie you, so come join my crew!

186
00:11:48,770 --> 00:11:49,810
Excuse me?!

187
00:11:49,810 --> 00:11:52,650
I'm looking for people
to join my pirate crew.

188
00:11:53,320 --> 00:11:54,650
Forget it!

189
00:11:54,650 --> 00:11:57,030
I'm not desperate enough
to become an outlaw!

190
00:11:57,030 --> 00:11:58,320
Screw that!

191
00:11:58,700 --> 00:12:00,570
What's wrong with being a pirate?!

192
00:12:00,570 --> 00:12:03,200
Who'd wanna be a pirate?
They're the lowest of the low!

193
00:12:03,200 --> 00:12:04,290
It's no big deal, right?

194
00:12:04,830 --> 00:12:08,250
You're already a
notorious bounty hunter!

195
00:12:08,710 --> 00:12:11,210
People can say whatever they want,

196
00:12:11,210 --> 00:12:13,710
but I've never done anything I regret.

197
00:12:14,590 --> 00:12:16,720
I will live through this…

198
00:12:17,300 --> 00:12:19,680
and make my dream a reality!

199
00:12:19,680 --> 00:12:21,850
Oh? I see.

200
00:12:22,220 --> 00:12:24,890
But I've already decided
that you're joining my crew!

201
00:12:24,890 --> 00:12:26,310
Like it's up to you!

202
00:12:26,310 --> 00:12:28,100
So you're a swordsman?

203
00:12:28,480 --> 00:12:32,440
Yeah, but Morgan's
idiot son took my gear...

204
00:12:32,440 --> 00:12:33,770
I'll go get it back for you!

205
00:12:33,770 --> 00:12:34,320
What?!

206
00:12:34,900 --> 00:12:37,860
You'll get your sword
when you join my crew!

207
00:12:37,860 --> 00:12:39,280
Don't screw with me!

208
00:12:41,200 --> 00:12:44,120
He's going in all by himself?!

209
00:12:53,340 --> 00:12:55,690
Alright! Keep it steady!

210
00:12:56,300 --> 00:12:58,220
Stand it up in one go!

211
00:12:59,380 --> 00:13:01,760
Daddy! Why aren't you
heading out to avenge me?!

212
00:13:01,760 --> 00:13:03,800
That guy hit me in the face!

213
00:13:03,800 --> 00:13:07,640
Not even you've done that!

214
00:13:07,640 --> 00:13:12,150
Do you know why I've
never hit you before?

215
00:13:12,150 --> 00:13:13,310
Do you?

216
00:13:13,310 --> 00:13:14,440
Sure...

217
00:13:14,440 --> 00:13:16,150
It's because I'm–

218
00:13:16,610 --> 00:13:17,900
Yes.

219
00:13:18,490 --> 00:13:20,400
Because you're...

220
00:13:27,330 --> 00:13:31,620
a hopeless son who's not even worth hitting!

221
00:13:32,250 --> 00:13:33,920
Let's get one thing straight!

222
00:13:37,250 --> 00:13:39,840
The only great one
around here is me!

223
00:13:39,840 --> 00:13:41,680
I'm great!

224
00:13:44,600 --> 00:13:48,680
By the way, I heard a rat snuck
into the crucifixion yard.

225
00:13:49,560 --> 00:13:53,190
I-I-I mean, there was that one runt,
but I saw to her punishment...

226
00:13:53,190 --> 00:13:54,650
You killed her, I hope?

227
00:13:54,650 --> 00:13:58,110
N-No! After all, she's still a little kid!

228
00:13:58,940 --> 00:14:00,650
You, there!

229
00:14:00,650 --> 00:14:02,280
Go to town and execute her!

230
00:14:02,650 --> 00:14:05,660
Y-You can't mean that, sir!
She's just a little girl!

231
00:14:05,660 --> 00:14:07,080
Even if it's an order...

232
00:14:07,620 --> 00:14:12,080
Anyone who disobeys my orders
is a traitor, even little brats.

233
00:14:12,080 --> 00:14:12,960
B-But...

234
00:14:13,830 --> 00:14:14,920
I can't do it!

235
00:14:19,920 --> 00:14:21,420
Lieutenant!

236
00:14:21,420 --> 00:14:23,180
Y-You didn't have to go that far!

237
00:14:23,930 --> 00:14:28,060
I ascended to the rank of captain
with nothing but my own strength.

238
00:14:28,680 --> 00:14:29,890
Listen up!

239
00:14:29,890 --> 00:14:32,020
In this world, rank is everything!

240
00:14:32,940 --> 00:14:36,650
Captain is the top rank on this base...

241
00:14:36,650 --> 00:14:40,130
And that makes me superior
to everyone here!

242
00:14:41,490 --> 00:14:45,420
In other words,
everything I do is right!

243
00:14:45,990 --> 00:14:47,570
Got that, you maggots?!

244
00:14:47,990 --> 00:14:49,700
– Yes, sir! Absolutely, sir!
– Yes, sir! Absolutely, sir!

245
00:14:50,160 --> 00:14:52,290
We can execute the brat later.

246
00:14:52,870 --> 00:14:53,790
Now watch!

247
00:14:53,790 --> 00:14:56,500
After years of construction,
it's finally complete!

248
00:14:56,920 --> 00:14:59,460
The symbol of my authority!

249
00:14:59,460 --> 00:15:01,420
Now, raise it up!

250
00:15:02,670 --> 00:15:06,180
Display my greatness
at the apex of this base!

251
00:15:09,640 --> 00:15:11,810
That's weird. There's no one here...

252
00:15:12,180 --> 00:15:15,640
I gotta find that idiot son
and get Zoro's sword back.

253
00:15:15,640 --> 00:15:16,440
Huh...?

254
00:15:17,310 --> 00:15:19,400
Pull! Pull!

255
00:15:24,610 --> 00:15:26,030
You there!

256
00:15:28,820 --> 00:15:30,330
You bumped it, didn't you?!

257
00:15:32,080 --> 00:15:34,140
I heard something up there...

258
00:15:35,080 --> 00:15:36,830
I-I'm sorry, sir!

259
00:15:36,830 --> 00:15:38,290
I was careless!

260
00:15:38,290 --> 00:15:42,300
I told you this statue embodies me!

261
00:15:42,300 --> 00:15:46,510
The slightest scratch or speck of dirt
is the same as treason!

262
00:15:46,510 --> 00:15:48,010
I'll check it out!

263
00:15:48,550 --> 00:15:50,180
Gum-Gum...

264
00:15:51,350 --> 00:15:52,760
Rocket!

265
00:15:52,760 --> 00:15:53,770
Now you'll pay!

266
00:15:55,390 --> 00:15:56,850
I jumped too far!

267
00:15:57,640 --> 00:15:58,770
What is that?!

268
00:15:58,770 --> 00:16:00,110
It flew up from below!

269
00:16:00,860 --> 00:16:02,270
Got it!

270
00:16:13,990 --> 00:16:15,000
Sorry...

271
00:16:17,710 --> 00:16:20,670
Seize him! I'll kill him myself!

272
00:16:20,670 --> 00:16:22,130
– Right away, sir!
– Right away, sir!

273
00:16:22,130 --> 00:16:24,630
Daddy! That's him! He's
the guy who punched me!

274
00:16:24,630 --> 00:16:25,670
Oh! It's you!

275
00:16:27,170 --> 00:16:28,430
I've been looking for you!

276
00:16:28,430 --> 00:16:30,970
Come with me! I need you
to return something!

277
00:16:31,640 --> 00:16:33,390
Let me go!

278
00:16:31,640 --> 00:16:33,390
– Master Helmeppo!
– Master Helmeppo!

279
00:16:33,390 --> 00:16:35,520
After him! Don't let him escape!

280
00:16:35,520 --> 00:16:37,810
Captain! Someone's
in the crucifixion yard!

281
00:16:37,810 --> 00:16:39,270
What?

282
00:16:44,070 --> 00:16:47,650
It's one traitor after another...

283
00:16:47,650 --> 00:16:49,610
You need to escape, Zoro!

284
00:16:49,610 --> 00:16:52,620
You'll be killed
for doing that, you know!

285
00:16:52,620 --> 00:16:55,450
I can't stand by and watch
Marines act like this!

286
00:16:55,450 --> 00:16:56,160
I...

287
00:16:56,830 --> 00:16:59,040
want to be an honorable Marine!

288
00:16:59,040 --> 00:17:03,250
Stop! I'm not running!
In just ten more days–

289
00:17:03,250 --> 00:17:05,460
Your execution is tomorrow!

290
00:17:05,460 --> 00:17:06,340
What?!

291
00:17:06,670 --> 00:17:11,430
Helmeppo never intended
to honor your agreement!

292
00:17:11,430 --> 00:17:15,970
So Luffy got angry and socked him!

293
00:17:15,970 --> 00:17:17,100
He did?

294
00:17:17,100 --> 00:17:20,980
And now the Marines are after Luffy.

295
00:17:20,980 --> 00:17:24,310
I won't ask you to be a pirate...

296
00:17:24,310 --> 00:17:28,440
but please, help Luffy!

297
00:17:32,240 --> 00:17:35,870
He's the only one who can save you.

298
00:17:37,040 --> 00:17:43,540
And I think, right now, you're
the only one who can save him.

299
00:17:45,090 --> 00:17:46,340
Stop right there!

300
00:17:50,050 --> 00:17:51,880
Where's Zoro's sword?!

301
00:17:51,880 --> 00:17:56,180
I-I'll tell you! I'll tell you!
Just stop dragging me!

302
00:17:56,180 --> 00:17:57,350
Alright! Tell me!

303
00:17:57,350 --> 00:18:00,600
In my room... We just passed it...

304
00:18:00,600 --> 00:18:02,480
What? Why didn't you say so?!

305
00:18:02,480 --> 00:18:04,060
Now we gotta go back.

306
00:18:04,060 --> 00:18:05,190
Halt!

307
00:18:05,190 --> 00:18:06,820
Release Master Helmeppo!

308
00:18:07,320 --> 00:18:08,320
No.

309
00:18:10,070 --> 00:18:12,070
Shoot if you want!

310
00:18:12,740 --> 00:18:14,160
No! Don't!

311
00:18:14,160 --> 00:18:15,950
Move it!

312
00:18:16,780 --> 00:18:18,830
For the crime of treason against me,

313
00:18:18,830 --> 00:18:22,000
I sentence the two of you to death!

314
00:18:24,920 --> 00:18:26,000
Is this the room?

315
00:18:29,920 --> 00:18:30,960
Over there!

316
00:18:31,970 --> 00:18:34,050
But there're three of them!

317
00:18:34,050 --> 00:18:35,930
Hey! Which sword is Zoro's?

318
00:18:36,600 --> 00:18:38,680
Oh, he passed out.

319
00:18:40,770 --> 00:18:41,680
Koby!

320
00:18:48,610 --> 00:18:52,570
You've caused
quite a disturbance here.

321
00:18:53,400 --> 00:18:57,320
You and that straw hat kid
are plotting a coup d'état, huh?

322
00:18:58,120 --> 00:19:00,580
I've always fought alone.

323
00:19:01,080 --> 00:19:05,040
Unlike a certain bastard who hides
behind his terrified flunkies!

324
00:19:05,040 --> 00:19:07,290
Roronoa Zoro...

325
00:19:07,290 --> 00:19:09,500
Don't you dare underestimate me!

326
00:19:10,000 --> 00:19:14,970
You may be strong, but that's
meaningless before my authority!

327
00:19:15,840 --> 00:19:17,010
Aim!

328
00:19:17,470 --> 00:19:18,720
I...

329
00:19:21,890 --> 00:19:25,600
can't afford to die here!

330
00:19:28,310 --> 00:19:30,730
Match over!

331
00:19:30,730 --> 00:19:34,240
The winner is Kuina,
with 2,000 wins and 0 losses!

332
00:19:34,240 --> 00:19:36,610
D-Damn it...

333
00:19:36,610 --> 00:19:39,240
You're as weak as ever, Zoro.

334
00:19:40,240 --> 00:19:43,700
Such a disappointment...
especially for a boy.

335
00:19:43,700 --> 00:19:46,080
Hey! Zoro isn't weak!

336
00:19:46,080 --> 00:19:47,960
He's the strongest guy here!

337
00:19:47,960 --> 00:19:49,580
He can even beat grown-ups!

338
00:19:49,580 --> 00:19:50,670
But...

339
00:19:50,670 --> 00:19:52,750
he's weaker than me.

340
00:19:53,130 --> 00:19:57,220
Even with two swords,
a weakling's still a weakling.

341
00:19:57,220 --> 00:19:59,430
Quit whining like little dogs.

342
00:19:59,430 --> 00:20:01,260
Losers like you should keep quiet.

343
00:20:10,770 --> 00:20:17,070
Another defeat, Zoro...
even after you've come so far.

344
00:20:17,450 --> 00:20:18,610
Sensei!

345
00:20:18,610 --> 00:20:22,490
Are you giving her secret training
'cause she's your daughter?!

346
00:20:22,490 --> 00:20:23,540
Don't cheat!

347
00:20:23,910 --> 00:20:26,660
No, no. Of course I'm not.

348
00:20:27,410 --> 00:20:30,290
Zoro has indeed improved...

349
00:20:30,290 --> 00:20:33,880
but Kuina has grown stronger as well.

350
00:20:34,380 --> 00:20:35,210
Zoro?

351
00:20:35,210 --> 00:20:36,380
Zoro...

352
00:20:36,380 --> 00:20:37,720
I'm gonna wash my face.

353
00:20:44,570 --> 00:20:45,430
Damn it!

354
00:20:46,270 --> 00:20:48,390
Why can't I beat Kuina?!

355
00:20:48,390 --> 00:20:50,060
Why?! Why?!

356
00:20:50,060 --> 00:20:52,860
I'm gonna be the world's
greatest swordsman!

357
00:20:52,860 --> 00:20:54,150
So why?!

358
00:21:05,240 --> 00:21:06,500
Zoro?!

359
00:21:06,500 --> 00:21:08,620
What are you doing out here?

360
00:21:08,620 --> 00:21:10,960
Right back at you!

361
00:21:10,960 --> 00:21:13,210
What are you doing
here at this hour?!

362
00:21:16,800 --> 00:21:19,930
I'm here to challenge you
to our 2,001st duel!

363
00:21:19,930 --> 00:21:23,140
I intend to make this our last fight!

364
00:21:23,680 --> 00:21:25,100
Let's end this!

365
00:21:25,100 --> 00:21:26,930
Fight me with a real sword!

366
00:21:27,470 --> 00:21:29,180
You have one, right?!

367
00:21:31,650 --> 00:21:32,940
Against me?

368
00:21:36,940 --> 00:21:38,070
Sure.

369
00:22:14,730 --> 00:22:17,020
My 2,001st win.

370
00:22:23,950 --> 00:22:26,620
Damn it!

371
00:22:27,160 --> 00:22:30,250
This sucks...

372
00:22:33,330 --> 00:22:36,420
I'm the one who should be crying.

373
00:22:37,540 --> 00:22:38,420
Huh?

374
00:22:39,550 --> 00:22:45,140
When girls grow up,
they become weaker than men.

375
00:22:46,010 --> 00:22:48,850
It won't be long before
even you catch up to me.

376
00:22:50,350 --> 00:22:54,940
Zoro, you always say you'll become
the world's greatest swordsman.

377
00:22:55,730 --> 00:23:00,980
But my father said that dream isn't
possible for me because I'm a girl.

378
00:23:02,320 --> 00:23:03,860
I understand...

379
00:23:03,860 --> 00:23:05,570
I understand that's how it is!

380
00:23:06,110 --> 00:23:08,780
But... But it's so frustrating!

381
00:23:09,330 --> 00:23:10,580
You're lucky, Zoro.

382
00:23:10,580 --> 00:23:11,790
You were born a boy.

383
00:23:12,790 --> 00:23:15,790
I want to be the world's
greatest swordsman too!

384
00:23:16,790 --> 00:23:19,500
My breasts are even starting to grow.

385
00:23:20,420 --> 00:23:23,920
If only... If only I had
been born a man...

386
00:23:25,470 --> 00:23:28,930
How can you cry like that
after you beat me?!

387
00:23:28,930 --> 00:23:32,430
It's not fair! You're my goal!

388
00:23:32,850 --> 00:23:33,770
Zoro...

389
00:23:33,770 --> 00:23:35,600
Boy this! Girl that!

390
00:23:35,600 --> 00:23:38,730
Is that gonna be your excuse
when I beat you someday?!

391
00:23:38,730 --> 00:23:41,020
You act like none of it is skill!

392
00:23:41,020 --> 00:23:44,400
You're insulting all my
hard training up till now!

393
00:23:44,820 --> 00:23:46,950
So enough of that crap!

394
00:23:49,490 --> 00:23:51,240
Promise me!

395
00:23:51,240 --> 00:23:55,120
Someday, one of us will be
the world's greatest swordsman!

396
00:23:55,870 --> 00:23:57,500
It's a race to see who makes it!

397
00:24:02,210 --> 00:24:03,840
You dummy.
You're so weak, and yet…

398
00:24:07,760 --> 00:24:09,510
– It's a promise!
– It's a promise!

399
00:24:13,100 --> 00:24:14,850
Gotta get stronger!

400
00:24:14,850 --> 00:24:17,140
Gotta hold more swords!

401
00:24:17,140 --> 00:24:19,400
If two's not enough, then I'll use three!

402
00:24:25,150 --> 00:24:26,900
What do you guys want?

403
00:24:29,410 --> 00:24:30,820
Kuina...

404
00:24:32,120 --> 00:24:34,620
Kuina's dead...

405
00:24:45,840 --> 00:24:50,180
Apparently, she slipped
and fell down the storehouse steps.

406
00:24:50,180 --> 00:24:51,050
The storehouse?

407
00:24:51,050 --> 00:24:55,930
She was looking for a whetstone
to sharpen her beloved sword.

408
00:24:55,930 --> 00:24:57,850
What would she need that for?

409
00:24:57,850 --> 00:24:59,600
I don't know...

410
00:24:59,600 --> 00:25:01,310
She was just a child too.

411
00:25:01,730 --> 00:25:04,110
Who knows why anyone
does anything...

412
00:25:04,110 --> 00:25:07,240
No one could predict
something like this.

413
00:25:16,240 --> 00:25:20,500
People are... such fragile things, Zoro.

414
00:25:32,590 --> 00:25:33,760
Sensei...

415
00:25:35,470 --> 00:25:37,140
That sword...

416
00:25:37,140 --> 00:25:38,850
Let me... have it.

417
00:25:41,350 --> 00:25:43,350
Kuina's sword?

418
00:25:44,310 --> 00:25:48,070
I'll get stronger
for the both of us now!

419
00:25:48,440 --> 00:25:51,860
I'll get so strong,
my name will reach the heavens!

420
00:25:52,610 --> 00:25:55,950
I'm gonna be the world's
greatest swordsman!

421
00:25:57,950 --> 00:26:00,660
I promised her...

422
00:26:01,210 --> 00:26:01,830
I...

423
00:26:10,420 --> 00:26:11,510
Very well. It's yours.

424
00:26:16,850 --> 00:26:21,810
I leave Kuina's spirit
and dreams... with you.

425
00:26:46,380 --> 00:26:48,750
Gum-Gum...

426
00:26:48,750 --> 00:26:49,920
Rocket!

427
00:26:49,920 --> 00:26:50,920
Fire!

428
00:26:54,880 --> 00:26:55,470
What're you–

429
00:26:55,470 --> 00:26:56,510
Luffy!

430
00:26:56,510 --> 00:26:57,140
Straw Hat?!

431
00:26:59,260 --> 00:27:00,470
No way...

432
00:27:02,810 --> 00:27:04,890
Nice try!

433
00:27:09,400 --> 00:27:11,900
I told you I was tough!

434
00:27:11,900 --> 00:27:15,070
Wh-Who the hell... are you?!

435
00:27:16,200 --> 00:27:18,580
I'm Monkey D. Luffy!

436
00:27:18,580 --> 00:27:20,830
The man who's gonna be
King of the Pirates!

437
00:04:35,670 --> 00:04:42,510
"Pirate Hunter" Roronoa Zoro

438
00:04:35,670 --> 00:04:42,510
"Pirate Hunter" Roronoa Zoro

439
00:05:58,800 --> 00:06:04,220
Helmeppo
Captain Morgan's Son

440
